<tr><td valign=top><img src="../../images/england.gif"></td>
<td valign=top><font face=arial><font size=+1><a name="uk">United Kingdom</a></font> - Through a network of consumer offices in England, Scotland, Wales, Northern Ireland and the Channel Islands, The Associates offers home equity-secured loans, unsecured personal loans and retail sales finance.<p>
The Associates also offers financing for transportation and industrial equipment.<p>
</td></tr>

<tr><td valign=top><img src="../../images/mexico.gif"></td>
<td valign=top><font face=arial><font size=+1><a name="mexico">Mexico</a></font> - Consumer financing includes personal loans as well as retail financing.  The Associates commercial operations in Mexico focus primarily on the construction, industrial, and transportation industries.<p>
</td></tr>

<tr><td valign=top><img src="../../images/canada.gif"></td>
<td valign=top><font face=arial><font size=+1><a name="canada">Canada</a></font> - Both commercial and consumer services are offered through a branch network throughout Canada.<p>
</td></tr>

<tr><td valign=top><img src="../../images/puertorico.gif"></td>
<td valign=top><font face=arial><font size=+1><a name="puertorico">Puerto Rico</a></font> - The Associates operation in Puerto Rico offers unsecured personal loans and real estate-secured loans.  Through a subsidiary, The Associates works with retailers to offer dealer finance packages for the purchase of goods and services.<p>
</td></tr>

<tr><td valign=top><img src="../../images/costarica.gif"></td>
<td valign=top><font face=arial><font size=+1><a name="costarica">Costa Rica</a></font> - A rapidly expanding branch network offers personal loans and loans for purchases of durable consumer goods, such as electronics equipment, furniture and appliances.<p>
</td></tr>

<tr><td valign=top><img src="../../images/taiwan.gif"></td>
<td valign=top><font face=arial><font size=+1><a name="taiwan">Taiwan</a></font> - The Taipei office gives the people of Taiwan access to credit by purchasing receivables for consumer goods such as electronic equipment, appliances, furniture, used vehicles and motorcycles.<p>
</td></tr>
	
